                            <comment id="12603454" author="techhusky" created="Mon, 9 Jun 2008 00:21:11 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Attached is &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/OPENJPA-545&quot; title=&quot;Replace UUID implementation with JDK 5 alternatives&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;OPENJPA-545&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;OPENJPA-545&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.patch, which provides type 4 UUID generators using standard Java 5 UUID support.  Two new generator types are defined to provide this support, &quot;uuid-type4-string&quot; and &quot;uuid-type4-hex&quot;.  Also included in the patch are jUnits and documentation updates.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Please review and provide comments.  Thanks!&lt;/p&gt;

